description.p:
The fragment is prepared by recognized phosphotriester methodology by which the following segments are prepared:


1) 5'-CTAGAGGGTATTAATAATGTATATTGATTTTAATAAGGAG-3';


2) 5'-GAATAATCATATGGATTTCCCAACCATTCCCCTC-3';


3) 5'-TCGAGAGGGGAATGGTTGGGAAATCCATATGATTATTCCTCCTT-3' and


4) 5'-ATTAAAATCAATATACATTATTAATACCCT-3'.
